Maintainer: GitHub <opensource+glb-director@github.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 12), dkms
Standards-Version: 4.5.0
Homepage: https://github.com/github/glb-director

Package: glb-redirect-iptables-dkms
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, dkms, pkg-config, libxtables12 | libxtables10, libxtables-dev | libxtables10
Description: GLB redirect iptables kernel module (DKMS)
 The ipt_GLBREDIRECT iptables target used by GitHub Load Balancer (GLB)
 directors to redirect packets to a secondary backend (the "second chance"
 design) without breaking established flows.
 .
 This package ships the module source and builds it on the target host via
 DKMS, and installs the matching libxt_GLBREDIRECT.so iptables extension.
